Peace remains elusive between Armenia and Azerbaijan
description: After more than three decades of conflict, a peace agreement between the two countries was announced in March. But Baku, currently in a position of strength, hesitates to sign. Near the border, Armenians, harboring no illusions, are torn between fears of a new offensive and a sense of defeat.

description: Tens of thousands of people took to the streets in several Brazilian cities on Sunday to protest the charges leveled against the former president, who faces up to 40 years in prison for an attempted coup d'état following his electoral defeat in 2022.

headline: Macabre video of the last hostages held by Hamas shocks Israel
description: The families of hostages are calling for an end to the war in order to negotiate the release of those still held captive. But the footage has also reinforced support for Benjamin Netanyahu's desire to prolong the war.

headline: AI is sowing discord in the world of fanfiction
description: Fanfiction authors often regard the emergence of AI-generated stories with suspicion, and the technology is shaking up the values within fan communities.

headline: Sydney Sweeney's American Eagle ad sparks controversy online and pleases Donald Trump
description: With a slogan playing on the ambiguity between 'genes' and 'jeans' − 'Sydney Sweeney has great jeans' − the actress has sparked controversy. Some have accused her of promoting eugenics, while President Donald Trump has come to American Eagle's defense, triggering a surge in its stock price.

description: On February 21, 2022, Nazarenko left Ukraine, thinking it was just for a weekend. The next day, Russia invaded her country. A few days later, she found herself in Lyon. Now 40 years old, she lives in Paris.

headline: Nevado del Ruiz, the explosive titan of the Andes
description: 'Of Volcanoes and Men' (2/6). French photographer Marguerite Bornhauser ventured onto the Colombian volcano, at an altitude of over 5,000 meters, in the summer of 2024. She captured the strangeness of its sculpted landscapes, using colored filters to highlight the fiery nature of our planet.

headline: Three erotic experiences inspired by boredom
description: Maïa Mazaurette is on a mission to spice up your steamy summer nights. This week, she suggests doing absolutely nothing – except letting your thoughts wander, caressing yourself for a long time and questioning your certainties.
